<hr class = "line-split">

<div class = "container-fluid">
	<div class = "row">
		<div class = "col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-3 about-us-text">
			<p>The auto repair industry is one of the least transparent consumer facing industries that exists. Most people will ask friends and family if they know any honest mechanics whenever their car breaks down. Anautomy is not here to send you quotes for your repair from nearby shops, you don't even know if any of those quotes are a fair price.</p> 
			<p>Anautomy is here to show you what other people are paying for their repairs and  where they got it done. Then you can determine if you are truly paying a fair price for a repair and get your car back on the road.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

